    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for relentless action in a top-down zombie shooter that blends strategic gameplay with survival against endless waves of zombies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position yourself wisely, manage your resources, and rely on skillful play to survive the onslaught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/f27fdfb00fca085a290f00bc839ebffc.poster.avif?t=1768419280\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/f27fdfb00fca085a290f00bc839ebffc.webm?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/f27fdfb00fca085a290f00bc839ebffc.mp4?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>End-of-Wave Buffs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each wave, choose from powerful buffs to tailor your playstyle and counter the increasing threats. Inspired by survivors-like mechanics, these upgrades can turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/43cff759a345618feb03ad5182325b2b.poster.avif?t=1768419280\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/43cff759a345618feb03ad5182325b2b.webm?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/43cff759a345618feb03ad5182325b2b.mp4?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Arsenal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between waves, open the shop to gear up. Purchase weapons, ammo, and equipment to stay ahead of the zombie onslaught and prepare for what’s next. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/cd49d1655b7b46da207525c2f02f6326.poster.avif?t=1768419280\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/cd49d1655b7b46da207525c2f02f6326.webm?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/cd49d1655b7b46da207525c2f02f6326.mp4?t=1768419280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
